ll's SKILL.md\n3. The agent follows the skill's instructions to complete the task\n\nSkills are detected automatically — you don't need to \"activate\" them. Just ask for something and if a skill matches, the agent uses it.\n\n---\n\n*Last updated: 2026-05-03*","oldText":"---\n\n*Last updated: 2026-05-03*"}],"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/skills-catalog.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":23398,"output":630,"cacheRead":129408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153436,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777845373253,"responseId":"0646f77d976962444295bb07f0992e26"}}
